wikipedia_page.main: Ronald Ebanks (born 21 April 1983 in the Cayman Islands) is a Cayman Islands cricketer. A right-handed batsman and right-arm medium-pace and off spin bowler, he has played for the Cayman Islands national cricket team since 2004.
